replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnUOGy9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbnUOGy9.png&h=ea09c098&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n眾籌買頭啦<br />\n自己做分分鐘失敗仲會有傷亡<br />\n公開件事，交比專業既黎，等各路江湖義士一個出手既借口<br />\n再推個波比Chinazi"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:20:17.000Z","msg":"冇眾籌平台比你籌，銀行會即時凍結，真人現金籌又比狗咬。<br />\n太隱蔽又籌唔到又有呃錢嘅機會，太揚又做唔到。<br />\n當你克服到上面嘅野，你比錢邊個買頭？<br />\n成日見人講暗網暗網但之前已經比人踢爆左大部分都係呃錢重會篤灰..."},{"pid":"270c498da73714e39f8462151a78320b62989ea8","tid":1592652,"uid":31511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:20:59.000Z","msg":"sorry ,幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[文宣工作]入黎揀個宣傳方法去做！重現69吹大雞！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1593328\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1593328</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>1.網絡宣傳+airdrop</strong></span><br />\n最易，亦都有好多巴絲做緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />辛苦哂<br />\n大家可以幫手post 去 fb,ig,twitter, <span style=\"color: red;\">仲有香討等各大論壇！</span>講真上得連登大部分都了解黎緊有咩活動，但仲有一大班人玩開其他論壇， 我建議可以用洗連登式洗各論壇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>2.各區連儂牆+各戶大廈𨋢口，洗樓</strong></span><br />\n連儂牆基本啦，唔洗多講，<span style=\"color: red;\">大家可以痴文宣係自己大廈𨋢口度，咁啲人等𨋢就睇到！</span> 最快靚正就痴係𨋢入邊，又或者攝係平時啲公告板入邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲可以痴𨋢門<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>3.痴各交通工具入邊</strong></span><br />\n開始有風險既一個做法，比人捉到會比人鬧，或觸犯唔知乜春例<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以揀d 陰濕位痴<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">例如番工番學準備定一兩張文宣痴好雙面膠，臨落車先痴</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>4.痴文宣上自己身，番工番學做流動宣傳</strong></span><br />\n難，難在恥力不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一般人唔慣痴野上身比人用異目睇，不過為左香港， i do<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可以痴係背脊或背囊，冇咁尷尬</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>5. 擺街站，派傳單</strong></span><br />\n最難，但都係最有效接觸到唔同類型既人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有安全風險，最好約埋幾個一齊做，揀人流多，未入夜既時間，事半功倍</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇少宣傳，多一個人做，效果雖然唔明顯，但如果多10萬個人做宣傳，個效果就好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家諗到其他方法都可以做，gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊copy 去其他post 比大家睇到"},{"pid":"b850483211f9ab08c774a9db4960ce5f91d923c2","tid":1592652,"uid":199523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfdb610ec696c94d7109b8733d7e701f74f044ff","tid":1592652,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:27:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ec0683aa2cc8d1d118dc170a1ed257741da4802","tid":1592652,"uid":293967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:29:38.000Z","msg":"之前唔係有葵芳狗比人斬到仆街?"},{"pid":"8c1b02a7163a7a42ce83ba76ae6a683284f69a70","tid":1592652,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:19:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d1091c25f19f057ea4fee26b0700a30b1a22f4","tid":1592652,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:52:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4674516d238e8cf55d992f7f272a4e05451906e8","tid":1592652,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:56:02.000Z","msg":"葵涌警署有一隻被斬到入icu啦"},{"pid":"0227c505706c93754b81dde5f9b01857b620d6fe","tid":1592652,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4674516d238e8cf55d992f7f272a4